text: Parygino () is a rural locality (a selo) in Karalatsky Selsoviet, Kamyzyaksky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 312 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 21 km SSE from Kamyzyak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kamyzyaksky District
title: Parygino
